  GET https://test.api.amadeus.com/v1/shopping/flight-offers?originLocationCode=SYD&destinationLocationCode=BKK&departureDate=2020-01-01&returnDate=2020-01-05&adults=2&currencyCode=AUD&includedAirlineCodes=TG&max=3
